_sText:
First map in a loooooong time :b Enjoy Goal: Eleminate the opposing team with preferably non-scope weapons since it's an aim map. Go go go ! :) Time spend on mapping: 2 hours. Time spend on compiling: 2 minutes, 30 seconds.

Asses/Comment/Stamp please.

 Also, please go to my profile and click the fancy watch button to be notified about more quality maps like this one. Cheers. I also do request! You can request a map from me anytime! Requirements for that: A sketch of what you want me to map / A detailed explanation of how the map will look like. Cost: Points :) If you wanna be notified about more map releases like this one, click this fancy button to watch me: But for now... adieu
